--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
SCOPE
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This License covers the framework (the "Software") — the original code of:

        BrokerSensorBridge/        (the user-mode broker + control service)
        BrokerSmbusDriver/         (the narrow KMDF kernel driver)
        scripts/                   (build / install / lifecycle tooling)
        docs/                      (design + reference documentation)
        root build tooling         (Build-All.ps1, etc.)

The Software reproduces publicly-documented hardware register maps and access
sequences that were verified against open-source reference drivers (the Linux
kernel hwmon / i2c subsystems). Hardware register facts are not themselves
copyrightable; no third-party source code or binary is distributed as part of
the Software. Attribution for every referenced project is in
THIRD-PARTY-NOTICES.md.

Any other directories that may exist in a local working copy are NOT part of the
Software and are NOT distributed under these terms.

